#Lemon Pasta with Shrimp

## Ingredients (2 people)
- Fusilli 500 g
- Lemon Zest from 2 lemons
- Garlic 5 cloves
- Cream 100 ml
- Vanamei Shrimp 200 g
- Butter 2 tsb
- Salt & Pepper to taste
- garden peas (optional)

##Instructions
1. Boil Pasta (Do this later if fresh pasta)
2. Grate garlic and lemon zest
3. Prepare Shrimp (peeled or not)
4. when pasta is almost ready - remove water & add everything
5. stir for 2 minutes



###Allergens 
- Wheat
- Seafood/Shellfish
- Lactose
